      <div class="msgContentFrame">if you plan to play solo or duo with a melee class, eventually you will have to lvl conj up to atleast lvl 16 for Protect/Shell which you MUST have, many enemies after lvl 25(mob lvl not your rank) including several R30 leve monsters will have skills that would hit you for about 800 on a tank and say 1200 on a healer or so, but with a Shell on you that goes down to 250-350 damage, which makes Protect and Shell a requirement for anybody. <br /> <br />But always remember not every monster you go lvl up on will require you to use shell/protect, there is always a mob you will find that does not ask you for those buffs to fight it.<div class="msgSig"><div class="msgSigBar sm">----------------------------</div><a href="HTTP://lodestone.finalfantasyxiv.com/rc/character/status?cicuid=4127062" rel="external nofollow" title="lodestone.finalfantasyxiv.com/rc/character/status?cicuid=4127062">Aggro Doctor's Rap Sheet</a> <br /><img src="http://common.zam.com/xivsigs/1815324.png" alt="Signature Image" border="0" /> <br /></div></div>
